23:17.272 --> 23:18.690
$75.

23:21.902 --> 23:23.671
- WOMAN: Ms. Israel!
- I hear they got Tom Clancy

23:23.695 --> 23:24.905
three million dollars

23:24.988 --> 23:27.532
