red-baiting propaganda.

23:27.616 --> 23:30.452
Lee, my morning has been
long enough already.

23:30.535 --> 23:32.204
He's a fraud.

23:32.287 --> 23:33.330
What's your point?

23:33.413 --> 23:36.083
He was drinking sherry
at your party.

23:36.166 --> 23:38.293
No self-respecting writer
would drink sherry.

23:38.418 --> 23:40.045
Oh, Lord, Lee.

23:40.295 --> 23:41.655
I need you to get me
a book advance

23:41.713 --> 23:43.548
on my Fanny Brice book.

23:43.632 --> 23:45.425
I need you to get
ten thousand dollars.

23:45.509 --> 23:48.512
I'm months behind in my rent,
and my cat is sick.

23:48.595 --> 23:50.573
And isn't this the exact reason
that I have an agent?

23:50.597 --> 23:52.933
I can't get you an advance
like that, Lee. I just can't.

23:53.391 --> 23:55.227
Give me one reason
why that cocky shit

23:55.352 --> 23:56.512
gets three million dollars...

23:56.645 --> 23:58.605
and you can't get me
ten thousand?

23:58.688 --> 23:59.898
Are you that bad of an agent?

24:00.190 --> 24:02.359
Toni, could you please
close the door?

24:02.442 --> 24:06.154
Ms. Israel and I have some
sensitive business to discuss.

24:06.321 --> 24:07.757
