of successful biographies

24:19.709 --> 24:20.895
and you've managed to disappear

24:20.919 --> 24:22.504
behind your subject matter,

24:22.587 --> 24:25.298
but because of that,
nobody knows who you are!

24:25.382 --> 24:27.134
Because I'm doing my job.

24:27.300 --> 24:28.300
Number two,

24:28.343 --> 24:30.137
