24:34.558 --> 24:36.518
Meanwhile, you have destroyed

24:36.601 --> 24:38.520
every bridge
I have built for you.

24:38.603 --> 24:41.523
See, that is beside the point.
I am doing good writing!

24:41.690 --> 24:44.818
Number three, nobody wants
a book about Fanny Brice.

24:44.985 --> 24:49.239
There is nothing new or sexy
about Fanny Brice.

24:49.322 --> 24:51.158
I couldn't get you a $10 advance

24:51.241 --> 24:52.951
for a book about Fanny Brice.

24:55.579 --> 24:58.456
I had a book on the
<i>New York Times</i> bestseller list.

24:59.457 --> 25:02.711
That has to count for something.

25:07.174 --> 25:10.177
Lee, I have known
you a long time,

25:10.260 --> 25:13.388
and believe me,
it hurts to say this to you.

25:13.471 --> 25:15.807
Tell me what to do then,
Marjorie.

25:15.891 --> 25:17.851
I have to do something.

25:17.934 --> 25:18.935
I'll take anything.

25:19.019 --> 25:21.188
Magazine pieces,
cracker box copy.

25:21.271 --> 25:25.192
Okay. Okay.
You have two options.

25:26.651 --> 25:28.111
You either become
a nicer person,

25:28.320 --> 25:31.406
you put on a clean shirt,
you stop drinking,

25:31.489 --> 25:33.241
you say "please"
and "thank you."

25:33.325 --> 25:35.619
Oh, God. Give me
a fucking break, please.

25:35.785 --> 25:38.705
Well, clearly that's
not going to happen.

25:38.788 --> 25:41.041
Or you can take
the time to go out

25:41.124 --> 25:43.126
and make a name for yourself.

25:43.293 --> 25:45.712
And then maybe, maybe,

25:45.795 --> 25:48.840
I can get you paid
for your work again.

25:48.924 --> 25:51.801
And how is it that I'm supposed
to do that, Marjorie?

25:51.885 --> 25:53.762
I'm a 51-year-old woman

25:53.845 --> 25:56.014
who likes cats
better than people.

25:57.015 --> 25:59.476
Not exactly hot and sexy,
as you like to say.

25:59.768 --> 26:01.561
Write your book
in your own voice.

26:01.645 --> 26:04.147
Well, you've been threatening
to do it for 10 years.

26:04.314 --> 26:06.399
I'd love to, Marjorie.

26:06.483 --> 26:08.568
Except that I have bills to pay.

26:08.735 --> 26:10.528
And not everybody
has an ex-husband

26:10.612 --> 26:13.073
who left them a
Classic Six on the Park!

26:16.076 --> 26:19.079
You can be an asshole
when you're famous,

26:19.162 --> 26:20.872
but as an unknown,

26:20.956 --> 26:23.959
you can't be such a bitch, Lee.

26:25.001 --> 26:27.045
Nobody is going to pay

26:27.128 --> 26:30.799
for the writer
Lee Israel right now.

26:30.882 --> 26:33.385
My suggestion to you
is you go out there

26:33.468 --> 26:36.346
and you find another way
to make a living.

26:48.441 --> 26:49.651
(sighs)

27:18.888 --> 27:19.888
Hmm.

27:30.775 --> 27:31.985
(Lee exhales)

27:33.528 --> 27:34.654
(typing)

27:34.738 --> 27:36.031
<i>LEE: "P.S.</i>

27:37.073 --> 27:41.369
<i>"I have a new grandkid,
